(June 24, 1954.)

(Republished.)

Henry B. Wesselman et al., as Executors of Blanche Wesselman, Deceased, Respondents, v. Engel Company, Inc., et al., Appellants, et al., Defendants.

Judgment, so far as appealed from, affirmed, with costs. No opinion. Present — Peck, P. J., Dore, Cohn, Callahan and Bastow, JJ.; Dore and Cohn, JJ., dissent; dissenting opinion by Dore, J. [See ante, p. 1020.]
